times.com/world/rest-of-world/11-mysterious-dots-on-a-2700-year-old-figurine-are-forcing-archaeologists-to-rethink-early-writing-in-guatemala/articleshow/131679766.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-12T15:15:16+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131680490,imgsize-37836.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UK to offer free Meningitis B vaccine to 1 million young people after deadly outbreaks]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131680259.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A major NHS programme will offer the meningitis B vaccine to around one million young people across the UK, including Year 13 students and those under 25 starting university. This initiative aims to protect vulnerable individuals entering environments where the disease spreads easily, following recent life-claiming outbreaks.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-to-offer-free-meningitis-b-vaccine-to-1-million-young-people-after-deadly-outbreaks/articleshow/131680259.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-to-offer-free-meningitis-b-vaccine-to-1-million-young-people-after-deadly-outbreaks/articleshow/131680259.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-12T15:08:59+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131680440,imgsize-39114.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘Suspected of espionage’: China confirms arrest of US citizen]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131680125.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/suspected-of-espionage-china-confirms-arrest-of-us-citizen/articleshow/131680125.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/suspected-of-espionage-china-confirms-arrest-of-us-citizen/articleshow/131680125.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-12T15:02:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131680223,imgsize-24322.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[EasyJet flight took off from wrong runway point at Manchester Airport after cockpit error]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131679778.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[An EasyJet flight from Manchester to Kos mistakenly took off from the wrong runway position, significantly reducing available runway length. While the Airbus A320 departed safely, investigators highlighted the serious safety implications of such navigation errors, especially under different conditions. The AAIB's findings emphasize the potential risks associated with reduced runway distance during take-off.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/easyjet-flight-took-off-from-wrong-runway-point-at-manchester-airport-after-cockpit-error/articleshow/131679778.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/easyjet-flight-took-off-from-wrong-runway-point-at-manchester-airport-after-cockpit-error/articleshow/131679778.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-12T14:39:53+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131679834,imgsize-69530.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Warren Buffett: “Time is the friend of the wonderful company, the enemy of…”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" styl