in Netanyahu by cancelling planned strikes against Iran and announcing a potential diplomatic deal within days. Trump claimed Iran's leadership approved a draft framework, aiming to extend a ceasefire and reopen the Strait of Hormuz. Netanyahu, reportedly caught off guard, had urged continued military pressure, highlighting growing differences over Iran policy.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/netanyahu-was-not-warned-in-advance-israeli-pm-blindsided-as-donald-trump-scrapped-iran-strike-plans/articleshow/131672809.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/netanyahu-was-not-warned-in-advance-israeli-pm-blindsided-as-donald-trump-scrapped-iran-strike-plans/articleshow/131672809.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-12T11:21:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131675284,imgsize-58020.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Lorry crashes into railway bridge in Warwickshire, disrupts key UK rail route; driver arrested]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131679808.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/major-disruption-on-uk-rail-network-after-lorry-smashes-into-warwickshire-bridge-driver-arrested/articleshow/131679808.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/major-disruption-on-uk-rail-network-after-lorry-smashes-into-warwickshire-bridge-driver-arrested/articleshow/131679808.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-12T14:43:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131679827,imgsize-131258.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Japan's struggl